Artificial Intelligence in the Workplace

    AI systems are becoming more prevalent in work environments.

    These systems offer powerful capabilities:

        Drug discovery
        Personalized product recommendations
        Fraud detection
        Introduction to AI Course

This course provides an overview of AI concepts and technologies.
You will learn:

    The principles of intelligent systems
    Common machine learning algorithms
    Artificial neural networks
    
AI and the Future of Work

    Non-technical professionals (managers, entrepreneurs, etc.) will increasingly interact with AI systems in their roles.
    Understanding AI will be crucial for leaders, just like understanding software is essential today.